my_anova <- aov_ez(data = data, dv = "anxiety", id = "participant", between = "group")

meta_model <- metacont(n_experimental,
         mean_experimental,
         sd_experimental,
         n_control,
         mean_control,
         sd_control,
         data = data_meta,
         studlab = paste(author),
         comb.fixed = FALSE,
         comb.random = TRUE,
         method.tau = "SJ",
         hakn = TRUE,
         prediction = TRUE,
         sm = "SMD")

forest(meta_model)
